</p>
<p>But, we might be overriding this in the bootstrap theme - so check there too. Yep,
we are: and this is where the <code>form-group</code> class comes from:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="a481536b94">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
