<h2 id="overriding-a-block">Overriding a Block <a class="headerlink" href="form-theme-validation-icon#overriding-a-block" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Ok! So... how can we override this? Very simple. First, copy the block. Second, go
to your templates directory and create a new file called <code>_formTheme.html.twig</code>.
The name of this isn't file is not important. And just so we know when this is working,
add a class: <code>cool-class</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="185a94ebb3">
