<p>But, where are those coming from? And what other stuff can we use?</p>
<p>It turns out that these are the <em>same</em> form variables that we can override from
the main, <code>_form.html.twig</code> template. Once you're inside of a form theme block, these
become <em>local</em> variables.</p>
<p>To see this in action, call <code>dump()</code> with no arguments:</p>
